<br>
Why, you ask?  I don't use a gun, so therefore I don't use the right.  <br>
<br>
True, but it's all about the ability.  I want to have the option to go out and purchase a firearm.  If I feel threatened, or hell if I feel like going out and shooting me deer for some deer steak.  The ability should be there.  That's what Freedom is all about, and that's what being an American is all about.  <br>
<br>
Clear it up at all?<br>
